OL,3,CMan who drove 100mph on motorway
OL,4,Cbefore falling asleep in live lane
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,FA motorist who drove at speeds of
OL,8,F100mph on the M4 in Berkshire before
OL,9,Ffalling asleep for 20 minutes in a
OL,10,Flive lane has avoided jail.
OL,12,FMaldini Fernandes, 31, of Southall,
OL,13,Fwas asleep at the wheel in the early
OL,14,Fhours of 18 January 2026.
OL,16,FMinutes earlier, he had been speeding,
OL,17,Fbefore coming to a stop in lanes 3 and
OL,18,F4 of the motorway.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
