PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773245482
OL,3,CMan who drove 100mph on motorway
OL,4,Cbefore falling asleep in live lane
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,FNo-one was seriously hurt in the
OL,8,Fincident, which unfolded between
OL,9,Fjunctions 9 and 11 of the M4.
OL,11,FFernandes was convicted of driving a
OL,12,Fvehicle in a dangerous manner and has
OL,13,Fbeen sentenced to 30 weeks in prison,
OL,14,Fsuspended for a year.
OL,16,FHe has also been disqualified from
OL,17,Fdriving for three years and has to do
OL,18,F150 hours of unpaid work.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
