OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773245482
OL,3,CMan who drove 100mph on motorway
OL,4,Cbefore falling asleep in live lane
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,FAlongside his driving offences,
OL,8,FFernandes failed to provide an
OL,9,Fevidential sample of breath in
OL,10,Fcustody, for which he was sentenced to
OL,11,F12 weeks in jail, also suspended for a
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FHe must pay over #200 in costs.
OL,16,FThames Valley Police's Roads Policing
OL,17,FTeam said: "Driving while tired puts
OL,18,Fyourself at others at huge risk.
OL,20,F"Please don't do it, it's not worth it.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
